    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that group, that was the first partisans was a begin to fight with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I think from that group now it's-- I don't know how many people know [? they ?] alive, because they must be in Israel.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
